---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-24 border-t border-paper-300 bg-paper-50">
  <div class="max-w-page mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-12 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-sm">
    <div>
      <h3 class="font-serif text-ink text-base mb-3">Qryptraveller's Notes</h3>
      <p class="text-ink-muted leading-relaxed">
        地球放浪２０年以上の旅人による、旅と思索の記録。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3 class="font-serif text-ink text-base mb-3">読み物</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-ink-muted">
        <li><a href="/series/" class="no-underline hover:text-ink">シリーズ一覧</a></li>
        <li><a href="/category/" class="no-underline hover:text-ink">カテゴリ一覧</a></li>
        <li><a href="/tag/" class="no-underline hover:text-ink">タグ一覧</a></li>
        <li><a href="/archive/" class="no-underline hover:text-ink">アーカイブ</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3 class="font-serif text-ink text-base mb-3">サイトについて</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-ink-muted">
        <li><a href="/about/" class="no-underline hover:text-ink">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="/rss.xml" class="no-underline hover:text-ink">RSSフィード</a></li>
        <li><a href="/sitemap-index.xml" class="no-underline hover:text-ink">サイトマップ</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="border-t border-paper-300">
    <div class="max-w-page mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-5 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-3 text-xs text-ink-muted">
      <span>© {year} Qryptraveller</span>
      <span class="italic font-serif">"Travel light, observe deeply."</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
